<plot>Inspired by her velosolex travels across Europe in her twenties, 78 year old Sybil Rampen forms a motorcycle gang of Grannies. They have a clubhouse, do TV shows, write a book and even travel to the famous biker congregation at Port Dover on Friday the 13th. Hell's Grannies it is about being ridiculous, taking chances and recognizing the value of life in all stages.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?234887</url></doc>
